ba0f5aa7d2f2d3fff971494e1a0fdd759a","tid":1561382,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2KzunBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2KzunBU.jpg&h=26c66f0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c59095783f4762662cf91088beb7b3c3b5cf570","tid":1561382,"uid":105578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:43:49.000Z","msg":"《香港&mdash;大英帝國的終章》<br />\n<br />\n我推薦依本，英國記者寫既。<br />\n<br />\n要睇香港歷史就最好唔好睇中國人寫既，佢地無論點寫總會有啲唔中立，同埋會有「香港係中國既」既諗法。"},{"pid":"d4c29e1c4d03f199834ee515eb7dee4b59a244e6","tid":1561382,"uid":221740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T15:48:33.000Z","msg":"香港史新編 王賡武<br />\n中國近代史 徐中約"},{"pid":"a035850b25f609743e07858ff617f0401cedd204","tid":1561382,"uid":167505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:17:06.000Z","msg":"柏楊白話版 資治通鑑"},{"pid":"69ec68dae7185f9b7cac4a206db79b806cea44b5","tid":1561382,"uid":176313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:04:39.000Z","msg":"傅樂城 中國通史<br />\n黃仁宇 中國大歷史"},{"pid":"63d685367bd396b5bdee81d745b885392559cac5","tid":1561382,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:19:28.000Z","msg":"純粹了解下係進程<br />\n<br />\nwiki 都夠你睇一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b162281e3636a3f37450a1b122593aeafaaa8705","tid":1561382,"uid":73406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:10:20.000Z","msg":"徐中約嗰本唔錯，雖然冗長（兩大本）但我覺得算係囊括整個近代中國史。一定要買繁體版，大陸版將中共之後嘅歷史盡數刊除，卑劣可恥<br />\n<br />\n其實近代史可能睇其他國家寫嘅會好啲，感覺上"},{"pid":"c1f537bdd4f7b7a6681ffdbba278db54a6d8fad0","tid":1561382,"uid":321846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T06:49:41.000Z","msg":"香港電台節目<br />\n中華五千年同埋古今風雲人物<br />\n 建築意 就講 香港城市面貌<br />\n<br />\n仲有個已經播完嘅神州唔知乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n台灣 Blog Gu shi<br />\n睇英文版的話， 睇下黃仁宇，如 萬曆十五年<br />\n<br />\n徐中約  rise of modern China<br />\n李劍農《 中國近百年政治史》"}]}